headline: Coty (COTY) Reports Q4 Loss, Beats Revenue Estimates
summary: Coty (COTY) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of -600.00% and +4.07%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
